{"tid":2409334,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"公大樹大恒大中文系邊個好啲","createTime":"2021-02-15T17:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T04:39:22.000Z","uid":370760,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf020f0473f4c050944bef57dd404ce9d6fe3a9","tid":2409334,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"借ac問，小弟成績平平但又想入中文系，但又怕唔夠分入八大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公大有普通嘅中文系，但都個雙學位嘅，包pgde，而且老師話身邊都有唔少公大出身嘅同事（教小學為多），如果考好啲入到雙學位嗰個都叫可以做下小學老師嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樹大中文系會教埋駢文，叫可以學多樣野，但聽講啲人出嚟都離不開做有關傳理嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇乜興趣<br />\n<br />\n恒大就唔係太清楚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求下大家幫小弟指點迷津"},{"pid":"8781acb93ca5fcfbe357e72fd3d64bc12fd6130c","tid":2409334,"uid":247946,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:15:38.000Z","msg":"樹大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9e815e7f2b5774366038b0dff71116c10c1a1e","tid":2409334,"uid":86246,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"中文呢3間一定係樹大啦<br />\n但讀中文做乜 想教書不如直接教大"},{"pid":"c1683795333cc0b69dec8b5acd48638d97bed102","tid":2409334,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8781acb93ca5fcfbe357e72fd3d64bc12fd6130c","tid":2409334,"uid":247946,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:15:38.000Z","msg":"樹大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"何解呢"},{"pid":"d24348bdc6a2f88daacdb0c479877db7d3e10957","tid":2409334,"uid":35603,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"認真答 <br />\n含大老師係幾好 普遍都有心教書"},{"pid":"20ed85e167e56cc4772879faf21925257ae9ab0c","tid":2409334,"uid":370760,"like":0,"d